      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup anywhere; it's a total dream to drive! I'd love for you to come by and see it for yourself\u2014I promise you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
