    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-grade example featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. Meticulously curated, the chassis exhibits zero subframe fatigue, and the high-revving inline-six has undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure mechanical longevity. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. Finished in Alpine White, this specimen retains factory paint depth and impeccable interior upholstery, representing a true collector-grade driving machine with peak mechanical harmony.",
      "price": 48500.0,
