      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standard. This car has been strictly stored in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather, which is evident in its flawless exterior. The paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no visible wear on the bolsters, and the original floor mats have been protected by weather-proof liners since day one. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It drives as tightly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. This is a rare opportunity to own a pristine, 'no-excuses' example for the most discerning buyer. All original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive service binder are included.",
